nodes.text: Darth Vader: Doctor Aphra 1 Halloween Comic Fest 2016

Darth Vader: Doctor Aphra 1 Halloween Comic Fest 2016 is a promotional one-shot comic book published by Marvel Comics for Halloween ComicFest 2016. Its story is a reprint of material originally published as Darth Vader 3.
